Ok...more info....For objs....set any item type that is type weapon
values 1 and 2 (v1 + v2) to 0. These  will be autogenerated based
on the weapons level. You may have only 5 weapons max that are your
own v1 and v2 values.
 
Now a word on dig.
------------------
You have to set the exflag (see help exflags) to CLOSED and DIG.
The following sector types will not allow digging to work:
city, inside, swim, noswim, underwater, and air.
Also to dig successfully the player must have a shovel. (ITEM_SHOVEL)
That sould do it.
~

